  "2026-07-19T16:09:08.865Z",codex-wide-sdk-20260719,"Repository adoption evidence: committed .gitattributes fence, clone-local merge-driver bootstrap guidance in AGENTS.md, CI fence audit, schema-triggered refresh diagnostics, merge docs, and SDK/CLI tests are implemented together. Fresh packed-package acceptance proved custom JSONL paths select pm-relationship, history paths select pm-history, and a divergent relationship stream merges into consecutive sequences 1,2,3. Full suite: 317 files, 5,975 tests, 100/100/100/100 coverage."
  "2026-07-19T16:15:17.435Z",codex-wide-sdk-20260719,"GitHub/repository health snapshot 2026-07-19: no pre-existing PR for this branch; GitHub Dependabot alerts=0 and secret-scanning alerts=0; pnpm audit=0 vulnerabilities. Seven open code-scanning alerts are existing OpenSSF Scorecard signals already mapped under canonical pm-gnzh children, so no duplicate items were created. The first linked tracker-read validation correctly failed its empty-schema context preflight; the test link now declares pm_context_mode=tracker and passed against a seeded 1,892-item copy with no mismatch. Direct repository validation reports merge_fence.status=ok, no duplicates, and no history drift."
